---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { GITHUB_REPO, SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<p>
				Fieldwork is a physical training environment for AI coding agents.
			</p>
			<p>
				Unlike simulated environments, we run on real chips and peripheral devices. This hardware cradle 
				exposes agents to the same challenges faced by embedded engineers: timing constraints, 
				communication protocols, hardware variability, noisy signals, and device-specific behavior. 
			</p>
			<p>
				Learn about some of the specific firmware cases we've developed for the benchmark on the blog 
				and follow along with our development.
			</p>
			<p>
				<a href="/blog">Read our blog here →</a>
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
